1 AN ACT
2 RELATING TO PUBLIC EDUCATION; ENACTING THE SPECIAL EDUCATION
3 ACT; CREATING THE OFFICE OF SPECIAL EDUCATION IN THE PUBLIC
4 EDUCATION DEPARTMENT; PROVIDING FOR A DEPUTY SECRETARY OF
5 SPECIAL EDUCATION; PROVIDING POWERS AND DUTIES; REMOVING
6 GIFTED STUDENTS FROM SPECIAL EDUCATION; RECOMPILING CURRENT
7 SPECIAL EDUCATION STATUTES INTO THE SPECIAL EDUCATION ACT;
8 AMENDING, REPEALING, ENACTING AND RECOMPILING SECTIONS OF THE
9 NMSA 1978.
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF NEW MEXICO:
12 SECTION 1. Section 22-1-2 NMSA 1978 (being Laws 2003,
